![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578167926771-1U5PU4330L371GJQ92O5/image-asset.jpeg)

The (DC)CW is BACK in a big way way! On this episode of Major Issues the guys go full on Arrowverse and discuss the current state of the DCEU just in time for a whole slew of premieres. Supergirl, Black Lightning, Legends of Tomorrow, Arrow and Flash have all made their mark in some way but what shows are really killing it right now? Also on this episode, we sink our teeth into the frst story of Flash's Rebirth run in 2016, Lightning Strikes Twice which marks the debut of one of the coolest modern villains ever, Godspeed!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
